scene.message:
Yukino: Excuse me! There are{nl}
demons out in the town!{nl}
Lots of people are hurt!{waitkey}Could you patrol...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Um{wait_fr:48}, officer?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Yukino, wait. There's{nl}
something wrong with that{nl}
man...!{waitkey}{ret}

Plenty of demons came, all{nl}
right. And look what they've{nl}
left me...{waitkey}{ret}

Officer's Ghost: Damn it...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Inspector...{wait_fr:32} please, help{nl}
me...{wait_fr:32} help...{waitkey}{ret}
